{"tid":36282,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"認真一問：三國時代，邊一個謀士你係覺得最聰明？","createTime":"2016-12-12T15:02:56.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-12T16:43:42.000Z","uid":60256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4f0705bca7e3f92b68074e1d3f535c2927d6297a","tid":36282,"uid":60256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T15:02:56.000Z","msg":"希望大家開完名之後講下少少理由點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我本人就覺得係賈翊，雖然唔太出名，但能夠係曹操之下明晳保身有幾多個？先幫張繡擊曹操，再利用張繡投靠曹操。成功在官渡打敗袁紹，平定北方。<br />\n曹操話如果郭嘉仲係到，赤壁唔會輸。但賈詡深知初定平方，人心未籠，加上軍隊由袁氏、劉表的敗軍之將組成。急戰未必會贏，倒不如坐山觀虎鬥，等待時機，惟曹操唔聽，導致大敗。<br />\n加上西涼之戰，成功用離間計平定西北方，令曹操安心攻打漢中。<br />\n最後更成功造王，令曹丕上位。<br />\n自己亦可以安享晚年。<br />\n想聽下大家意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8a5ec1aeff66d3fea189e4b62c9106a103419a2","tid":36282,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T15:04:40.000Z","msg":"雲長老婆"},{"pid":"aa638c7e3cd9a7625bffc2d871842c78ddfb2c02","tid":36282,"uid":9531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T15:05:25.000Z","msg":"周瑜子公謹"},{"pid":"888f4fba025202e0df3c09f64bfa836fff405cdf","tid":36282,"uid":9531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T15:05:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>周瑜字公謹</blockquote>"},{"pid":"0da28b7a8eba0a5315e6c4a0c55c457bd27cfca3","tid":36282,"uid":28052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T15:06:28.000Z","msg":"呂蒙"},{"pid":"7c680eb7eac21332c59c0f895881d935c7acc075","tid":36282,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T15:08:28.000Z","msg":"司馬雲信"},{"pid":"302c23c6c596a4affa9e2e0eadb7cc3dfc37b9df","tid":36282,"uid":18867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T15:08:29.000Z","msg":"始終都係孔明 事跡例證多到唔知從何說起 不如唔講 梳狗"},{"pid":"fe317c56a50d5083af25ce31cbd5cad097a8f70f","tid":36282,"uid":64325,"like":0,"dislike":0